  }, "ChatGPT Contributions"), mdx("p", null, "Given one of the prominently employed social attack vectors is to seek to debase the merit of a persons words and/or ability to be heard or be socially supported to be listened to; the use of ChatGPT has been used fairly extensively; including contributions for this topic also"), mdx("p", null, "Below is some content that has been generated by ChatGPT.   "), mdx("p", null, "There are a number of social attack vectors or behaviors that can negatively impact knowledge workers who are working online. Some examples include:"), mdx("ol", null, mdx("li", {
